{"id": "1436688254135959674", "channel_id": "1436370496181506159", "type": 0, "author_id": "317871635736690698", "author_name": "thigh_god.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Bump", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T12:06:12.163000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436370496181506159", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Lightless realm expansion", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1436574373992726708", "channel_id": "1436574373992726708", "type": 0, "author_id": "1403431686116741143", "author_name": "2300011747", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'm a loyal Morimens player, and there are some areas where the recent anniversary events need improvement. I urge the Biav team to listen to player feedback and avoid such a rushed ending to the second anniversary celebration:\n\n1. Continue the anniversary tradition of giving away +12 limited-edition Destiny Wheels. This is both a tradition and genuinely helpful to players.\n\n2. Add more anniversary events. The current preview events hardly qualify as anniversary events; they're virtually identical to other versions except for the permanent benefits and changes. While the Biav team's optimizations are good, this isn't what an anniversary version should include. Where are the extra anniversary events that should have been included? Please add them back.\n\n3. Make the \"Time reversal\" feature free. This is a fundamental game feature optimization issue and shouldn't be just a benefit for paying players.\n\nAs players, we genuinely hope that Morimens will continue to improve, but the current state is truly worrying. We sincerely hope that the Biav team can listen to the players' opinions and work together to create a better Morimens. Please!", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T04:33:41.021000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "❌", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436574373992726708", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」2nd anniversary suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
