{"id": "1436613518001573908", "channel_id": "1436574373992726708", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:dead:1356082627509092372>", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T07:09:13.680000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436574373992726708", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」2nd anniversary suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1436625174781759518", "channel_id": "1436574373992726708", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "Yeah, and it can be pretty justified, the problem is that they do were straggling most of the time, gradual decline in recourses for the first year until almost eos, and then slow recovery from there up until now, the fact that they had to rebuild the team an update the game to make it more generally accessible it must have syphon a lot of time.\nI think this is a potential turning point, they have updated the base structure of the game to accommodate the rest of the second arc, so i will expect a better stream of new content from now on.\nWe will see, and at the end of the day, if they can't deliver after this point, players will have all the reason to leave if not satisfied.", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T07:55:32.873000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-08T07:56:13.304000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436574373992726708", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」2nd anniversary suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
