{"id": "1436817744141226085", "channel_id": "1436817744141226085", "type": 0, "author_id": "337260387554557953", "author_name": "happyskull", "author_bot": false, "content": "Device:\nIOS and Windows\n\nIn-game UserID:\n101002861\n\nBug description:\nVery often when Hydra does this attack, the snake that appears in the attack animation gets stuck on the screen. On my phone this happens every single time, on Windows computer it's more like 50/50 chance.\n\nOn Windows, sometimes the bug will fix itself after Hydra does the same attack again, but not always.", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T20:40:44.986000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1436817744912842752", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1345244, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1436817744141226085/1436817744912842752/image.png?ex=69cc314d&is=69cadfcd&hm=14afb6ba08bbbc3cc1b257fa81dab15bb2d0297e1e40767407b0f0af464341d3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436817744141226085", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Hydra weekly boss attack bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1436668588860641360", "channel_id": "1436668588860641360", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "To replicate:\n1. Have a team loadout with an empty team slot.\n2. Click on the empty team slot.\n3. Find and tap on a character that is E0.\n\nExpected behavior: E0 is shown on the right\nActual behavior: E3 is shown on the right\n\nIt seems to do with there being no other Enlighten character selected beforehand, since it stops after clicking on someone non-E0 or having someone in team slot.", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T10:48:03.596000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1436668589615878174", "filename": "SxWGBMn.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1507259, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1436668588860641360/1436668589615878174/SxWGBMn.png?ex=69cba663&is=69ca54e3&hm=47fd16e281bcaef24dcdc1997eadc9ae9457c9c3169aad6d2cabcfe5c35b5d65&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436668588860641360", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」E0 character shows up as E3 in preview", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
